added.title: Super Screen Cleaners
added.description: Thomas pretends to be a hero to help ensure the movie screen Nia's delivering arrives clean and pristine.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Overnight Stop
added.description: Percy feels anxious about spending a night away from home during an overnight delivery with Thomas and Nia.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Caillou Goes to the Car Wash/Far Away Home/All You Can Eat/Caillou Stays Up Late
added.description: Caillou, Dad and Rosie take the car to the car wash./Caillou uses his imagination to turn the house into the setting for a desert expedition./Caillou and Mom are joining Clementine and her mom for a picnic./Caillou finds out his parents are having a grown-up party.

added.title: Backyard Zoo/Caillou's Scavenger Hunt/Too Many Cooks/The Berry Patch
added.description: Caillou and Clementine and Leo make their own zoo in the backyard./When Julie comes over to babysit she announces that she's brought along a really fun game./Caillou's babysitter is late./Caillou spends a day strawberry picking.

added.title: Caillou's Suitcase/Try, Try Again/The New Leaf/Happy New Year
added.description: Caillou's very excited about a family trip and decides to pack his own suitcase./Caillou has trouble learning to tie his shoelaces./Caillou, Grandpa and Dad go for a special hike in the woods./Caillou celebrates Chinese New Year.

added.title: Caillou's Teddy Shirt/Caillou Meets Robbie/The Pinata/Caillou's Promise
added.description: Caillou's favorite shirt has teddy bears on it./Caillou introduces himself to another little boy at the park./Caillou can't wait for the mailman to deliver his invitation to his friend Xavier's party./Caillou learns about keeping promises.

added.title: A Surprise for Mommy/Caillou Misses Sarah/T-Shirt Trouble/A Helping Hand
added.description: Dad gets a professional photo of Caillou and Rosie./Caillou's friend Sarah is going away on a trip for two whole weeks./Caillou's brand new T-shirt is ruined by grape juice./Caillou and Grandma, along with Rover the dog, spend a day at a retirement home.

added.title: The Snake Dance
added.description: When Mush-Mush and Chep lose Lilit's flying disc down a snake tunnel, he is confident he can get it back. All animals love Chep and no one knows more about snakes than he does. But this snake is not to be messed with! When they finally sneak into the snake tunnel, they learn why the snake has been acting so strangely…

added.title: Lost
added.description: Bing and Flop are in the park with Hoppity. What will happen when Bing finds some dog poo?

added.title: The Birthday That Wasn't
added.description: Dibble misunderstands the Bears' intentions when they secretly make a plush toy Whiffle for her "Un-birthday." Thinking it's real and that the Bears love it more than they love her, she steals it and plans to leave it in the forest. She has second thoughts and returns her "rival" to her friends, only to learn that it's a gift to show their love for her.

added.title: Bird Call
added.description: Chanterelle has built a whistle that can reproduce the most beautiful sound of the forest: the one of the Nightingale. When the whistle disappears, Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit soon discover that it has been stolen by a beetle. In order to finally hear what a real Nightingale sounds like, they'll have to get it back!

added.title: Picnic
added.description: It's picnic time! Bing and Flop are getting ready to have a picnic, but will they remember to bring everything they need?

added.title: The Big Rumble
added.description: A family of comically raucous rocks moves in near a Whiffle garden and drives them to distraction with their ground-pounding games. Funshine gets the rocks to leave. But when he learns their ground-pounding creates new soil, he must convince them to come back.

added.title: Do You Speak Dance/A New Spider in Town/Dollhouse Mates
added.description: "Maizie" keeps ignoring Lucas and Findley, but not only do they learn she has a cousin, they also learn a new skill!/ Lucas befriends a bright purple toy spider, and Findley gets jealous./ Lucas and Findley move into the dollhouse together.

added.title: Lucas We Have a Problem/Egg-Scuse Me/Pokey Dokey
added.description: Lucas helps Bodhi fulfill her dream of touching a star./ Lucas finds an egg and decides to take care of it. But he learns that responsibility is hard./ When Avocado loses her beloved toy, Lucas and Findley are determined to cheer her up.

added.title: Flower Power
added.description: The babies all want to pick the best flowers for Granny but they end up destroying her garden.

added.title: Elly Spots
added.description: Elly is stricken with a case of the Elly Spots, and Pato and Pocoyo have to forsake their picnic to look after her. Once she is better, she makes it up to them.

added.title: Lightning Bugs Sylvester
added.description: Sylvester learns to overcome his fear of lightning.

added.title: Up Up and Away
added.description: Our friends are playing with a model airplane which shoots off up into space. They go on an adventure to retrieve the beloved toy, encountering some friendly, bendy aliens along the way.

added.title: A Surprise for Pocoyo
added.description: Pocoyo's friends decide to give him a surprise party - simply to show him how much they love him.

added.title: Having a Ball
added.description: Pocoyo and Pato are enjoying playing with their new ball. But all of a sudden, the ball takes on a life of its own, and Pocoyo and Pato have to chase it. Who's got the ball…? It's Baby Bird who just wants to play too!

added.title: Super Pocoyo
added.description: Today Pocoyo is Super Pocoyo - a superhero determined to rescue his friends from tight fixes - even when they don't need to be rescued.

removed.title: Bruce Bunny
removed.description: When Daffy starts making up hurtful rhymes, Bugs changes his name to Bruce.

removed.title: A Wish-Full Reunion
removed.description: Mysterious flying hearts appear in Care-A-Lot and bring Wish Bear to the Silver Lining. She joins the Care Bears on a mission to bring a mystical mother bird's missing baby chicks home, and give a new home to an orphan bird.

removed.title: Boingo
removed.description: Lucas, Findley and Bodhi become obsessed with a new toy called Boingo.

removed.title: Pato's Postal Service
removed.description: When Pocoyo wants to send a letter to Elly, Pato embraces the very important role of postman. After much to-ing and fro-ing, Pato delivers a mammoth package!

removed.title: An Almost Eggless Easter
removed.description: When the Easter Bunny's beautifully-painted eggs are drained of their color, it looks like Dibble will miss her first Easter egg hunt - she's really been looking forward to it. The Bears must find a way to repaint all the eggs before the big day.

removed.title: Who's Eating Mushton
removed.description: Everyone in Mushton is finding that their precious wooden things are being munched and destroyed by someone or something. All the evidence points toward Truff's new woodworm pet Chompski. But Truff refuses to believe Chompski would do such a thing! It's up to Chep, Lilit and Mush-Mush to convince Truff. But first they have to catch Chompski in the act!

removed.title: Mystery Boxcars
removed.description: Kana is upset when she keeps running out of power, but a mystery scavenger hunt is just the thing to cheer her up.
removed.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

removed.title: Capture the Flag
removed.description: When Percy loses Nia's parade flag before the big parade, Thomas helps them search for it before the event begins.
removed.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

removed.title: Leader of the Pack
removed.description: Daffy starts a secret password club for everyone except Bugs.

removed.description: Caillou helps Grandma put together a belated surprise party./After a scary nightmare, Caillou doesn't want to sleep in his own bed./Caillou's very excited when Dad brings home a computer./While playing dinosaurs in the backyard, Caillou and Leo dig up a fish fossil rock.

removed.title: Comic Caper!/Hide and Seek/Caillou's Clouds/Caillou Cleans Up
removed.description: Caillou and Dad are settling down for their favorite weekend ritual of "reading" the paper./Caillou can't seem to play quietly in his room without Rosie interrupting./Caillou, Mom and Rosie go to the park for a picnic and bring a kite./Mom and Dad are busy with spring cleaning and Caillou wants to help.

removed.title: Hiccup
removed.description: Pato gets the hiccups. Together Pocoyo, Elly and Loula help him to get rid of them by giving him a surprise.

removed.title: Caillou and the Tooth Fairy/I Want to Grow Up/Caillou's Big Chill/Leo's Hamster
removed.description: Caillou and Sarah are playing together when Caillou notices his friend wiggling her loose tooth back and forth./Caillou wants to be taller like his friend Andre and tries to think of a way to grow faster./Caillou is excited about the arrival of spring./Caillou loves Leo's pet hamster and would really like to have his own.

removed.title: Train
removed.description: Bing's train can do lots of great things in the park's playground, but as Bing and Pando climb higher, what else will the train do?

removed.title: My Muddy Buddy
removed.description: When Lilit creates a 'friends tree' mapping out who everyone is best friends with in Mushton, she realizes Muddler has no friends at all. Unable to accept this, Lilit slips away to try and befriend him. But Muddler's perception of friendship is somewhat unique, meaning Lilit now needs the help of her two best friends, Mush-Mush and Chep, to escape from Muddler's clutches.

removed.title: Puppy Love
removed.description: Pocoyo neglects Loula when he finds a toy dog to play with.

removed.title: Say Goodbye
removed.description: Bing and Sula are having so much fun playing together, they don't want to say goodbye. What will happen when Amma comes to collect Sula?

removed.title: Twinkle Twinkle
removed.description: Elly finds a beautiful star that has fallen out of the night sky. She loves it and wants to keep it for herself. But Pocoyo makes her realize that the star is for everyone to enjoy. Together they put it back where it's meant to be.

removed.title: Bat and Ball
removed.description: It's time for a game of Bat and Ball with Octopus. Everyone wants to have a turn at batting, but the friends learn that you have to wait your turn.

removed.title: Findley's Bad Day
